tourBios.curYrHigh: Finished T33 at the Mainland China Qualifying Tournament in early March at Wolong Lake GC in Liuzhou to secure conditionally-exempt playing privileges for the season.
tourBios.carHigh: 2014: In three PGA TOUR China Series' starts, made one cut—at the United Investment Real Estate Wuhan Open, where he finished 71st.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA Tour China Serie was 71st in 2014 at the United Investment Real Estate Wuhan Open.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T11th in Victory Leaders on the PGA Tour China Series.
